//TODO: sampler info
//TODO: maybe add scene header

for each mesh:

name (null terminated string)
bin uri (null terminated string)
diffuse texture uri (null terminated string)
metallic/roughness/occlusion texture uri (null terminated string)
normal texture uri (null terminated string)
emissive texture uri (null terminated string)
texcoord buffer info:
    buffer offset (U32)
    buffer size (U32)
normal buffer info:
    buffer offset (U32)
    buffer size (U32)
tangent buffer info:
    buffer offset (U32)
    buffer size (U32)
position buffer info:
    buffer offset (U32)
    buffer size (U32)
material info:
    base color factor (RGBA F32)
    metallic factor (F32)
    roughness factor (F32)
    occlusion factor (F32)
    alpha mode (U8) 0 = opaque, 1 = mask, 2 = transparent
    alpha cutoff (F32)
mesh info:
    position (XYZ F32)
    rotation (XYZ F32)
    scale (XYZ F32)